Wednesday, February 15, 1989

MERIT DOCKET

87-1572. Bowman v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio, No. 83-1328-GA-CSS. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
